<plot>Lakis and Vaso are in love and intend to get married. Vaso's brother, however, protests because he would prefer Giagkos as his brother-in-law, a poor, honest, hard-working man who is in love with Vaso. Lakis leaves for Canada, and Vaso marries Giagkos, who gets involved with criminals and ends up in jail. While Giagkos is in jail, Lakis returns from Canada, looks for Vaso and persuades her to leave her home and child and go with him. Giagkos is released from jail, learns the news but is not daunted. He searches for his loved one, finds her, and they reunite for good.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?025640</url></doc>
